{"tid":1728040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"職業升級-鑽地師","createTime":"2019-11-16T16:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:50:25.000Z","uid":301915,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"50e4b9247424645bd6710434af33e8e416705833","tid":1728040,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:47:38.000Z","msg":"我地鑽又好，鑿又好，破壞主要交通幹道，如紅隧D路。<br />\n咁做有咩好處?<br />\n首先，省力。你一次過炸毀條路，點都易過般野啊?<br />\n然後，堵路效果一流。D車點過?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，最重要!佢一定整唔返。</span></strong></strong></span>佢地根本修唔到。朝早就佢要封路修理，幫埋我地封路。晚上，佢夠膽係夜媽媽修?唔驚神獸?<br />\n所以，職業已正開放，請各香城online玩家考慮升級，遊戲體驗一流!"},{"pid":"d27c6c027c7821f2b956024a1f5a2a400b1be7db","tid":1728040,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:47:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b6c33a7b218116966999ccb45a7752178e6f537","tid":1728040,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"升級啊"},{"pid":"134ae7df8f548cb9d3020a8c9abc1e0d91b656ac","tid":1728040,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"有無人???"},{"pid":"17fd2c006643a5c18fd899d80c94fef0d0c20206","tid":1728040,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:49:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4c00a069d1f34af455ddcb49d61e0bacf114b97","tid":1728040,"uid":46430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcd70b139f3ea6e7fb846f3503660d2c498e647","tid":1728040,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"真心覺得可以從此level up"},{"pid":"24db55c237401bf25f49462dcc0a2735067b2321","tid":1728040,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"好正經架"},{"pid":"ee3f0bdff716652a1cf49a5a437a51be8c18f8d5